16. [출제의도] 담화의 특정 정보 파악하기
W: Hello, students. The National Photography 
Association announced that it’ll hold the 5th 
Great Nature Photo Contest. Any photos about 
nature will be okay. You can easily participate 
in the contest by uploading your photos on the 
homepage. The registration period is from 
March 1 to April 15. Winners will be 
announced on April 30 through the homepage. 
They will get a trophy and a prize. Except for 
the previous winners, anyone can participate in 
the contest. For more information, you can visit 
the homepage at www.greatnaturecontest.com.
17. [출제의도] 대화의 특정 정보 파악하기
M: Is there anything I can do for you, ma’am?
W: Well, I want to buy a new smartphone.
M: Do you have any special brand in mind?
W: No. I can’t decide which one to buy.
M: Then, let me help you. Look at this chart. I 
think a screen size over 5 inches is 
inconvenient to carry.
W: Yeah, I want a convenient one.
M: Okay. How about pixels? If you want quality 
photos, you need high pixels.
W: Pixels are not that important to me. 
M: Then, what price range do you want?
W: It should be less than $200.
M: Okay, ma’am. Now you have only two options.
W: I’ll take the cheaper one.
